The Furhaven pet gates are a simple way to contain your pets.  Our patent pending stability leg design allows the 3-panel hinged gate to be full extended to a maximum width of 48 inches without tipping over. Gates also have non-skid pads to help protect floors.  These fold-and-go gates are perfect to take to grandmas house.  Just fold the gate to their compact size and toss then into your car for portable containment.